            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>&nbsp;</td>
            <td>7. faster coagulation time of blood</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>&nbsp;</td>
            <td>8. increased mental activity</td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>Reference: Guyton, <em>Basic Human Physiology</em><br />
W.B. Saunders, Philadelphia, 1971<br />
​pp. 497-502</p>
														</div>


				
